On the other hand, the flight to the official mission of the Prime Minister and the marshals of the Sejm and the Senate will only be carried out "in order to carry out tasks directly related to the function".
The Act also specifies the list of persons who can accompany the most important persons in the country during flight.
According to the rules on board the aircraft, the members of the delegation may be invited Members, Senators, representatives of the public authorities and experts; persons providing technical, medical or organisational services; and journalists.
